The paper proposes an algorithm for constructing confidence sets for deep neural networks with PAC guarantees, which is a topic related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The algorithm is demonstrated on ResNet for ImageNet, a visual object tracking model, and a dynamics model for the half-cheetah reinforcement learning problem, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV) and reinforcement learning (cs.NE, cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.CV, followed by cs.NE and cs.SY.
